Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're listening in on this conversation.\NBut I need to tell all Mages out there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Mage Academy is on the move!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In Eramu, they're carrying out a large-scale purge\Nfor Mages supporting the Lords.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once they heard\Nof the new emperor's ascension,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Mage Academy\Nchose to war with the Lords.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They are now an enemy to the Lords.\NThere's no room to negotiate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Grancrest must be\Nthat great of a threat to the Mage Academy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When this transmission ends,\Nbreak your wands!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're tracking our whereabouts\Nthrough the Chaos Globe set in our wands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We should assume that all conversations\Nthrough them are being monitored.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The darkness within the Mage Academy\Nis deeper than you think.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, that darkness may be\Nthe Academy's true essence!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, we received a message sent\Nto all Mages about a disturbance in Eramu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they're purging every Mage\Nthought to be an ally of the Lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because Sir Theo\Nascended to the throne as emperor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Because of that, the birth of the Grancrest\Nhas become a certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, along with the Emperor, the Mage Academy\Nhas deemed all the Lords as an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight the Mage Academy in Eramu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the plan going forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From hereon, we'll consolidate the Treaty, Union,\Nand Alliance forces, and form the Imperial Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow afternoon, the Imperial Army\Nwill march on Eramu to quell the disturbance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That said, the Mage Academy\Nwill be a formidable opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can assume it'll be a grueling battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to be in this battle,\Nyou'll be permitted to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please think it over carefully before we leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What will you Mages do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have pledged my eternal loyalty to Sir Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will accompany him wherever he goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Mage's job is first and foremost\Nto serve his Lord. That will not change for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't very well abandon Sir Selge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Lassic is a Lord well worth serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Above all, he holds my skills in high esteem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:05:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Eudokia may be an uninhibited free spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but she's extremely kind,\Nand as pure-hearted as a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So much that she can\Neven embrace immorality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly can't betray such a person's trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're a Mage,\Nit's only natural to comply with the Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Faustio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this,\NI have no choice but to void our contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, but I'll be returning to Eramu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You served me well for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are grateful to those who stayed behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have an important favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:05:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those wands in your hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please break them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Break our wands?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we do that, we can't cast any magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it'll become more difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But these wands
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are capable of notifying the Mage Academy\Nof our location through the Chaos Globes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, it seems the Academy can listen in\Non everything we say through these wands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,\Nthen we shouldn't be using them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let the destruction of our wands serve as proof\Nof our secession from the Mage Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Around one-third of the Union and Alliance Lords\Nare preparing to return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably 50,000 will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:07:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Around one-third of the Mages\Nhave returned to Eramu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't avoid a decline in our forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's more than expected, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Were the wands completely destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had everyone who stayed behind\Ndestroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no fear of the Mage Academy\Neavesdropping on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can still wield magic without our wands,\Nbut not being able to communicate is painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Sir Theo has become emperor,\Nyou're the Imperial Army's Mage Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than being in low spirits, you should\Ndevise a way to communicate without wands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally getting the chance\Nto work with you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but as your superior!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:07:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aishela!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't you join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Come on, Aishela!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Are you still holding a grudge about that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Of course!\NI can never forget that he almost killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's true, at that incident,\NI came close to being eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}After all, as a Mage school student, I was\Na troublemaker and always broke the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like setting that cat free\Nin the magical beast zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's rude of you to call me a cat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}But you purr when we pet your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}To think that you nearly died for this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I couldn't stand seeing Sir Balgyary\Nlocked up in a cage like a prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The principal was the most adamant\Nabout eliminating you that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then this guy\Ndidn't even veto that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He chose to abide by the rules\Ninstead of protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you protected me too, right, Aishela?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it, you had already\Ntaken me somewhere with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're my cute little sister.\NOf course I'd protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he should've done, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}But that's all in the past,\Nand as you can see, I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And after the punishment was dropped,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:10:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Father held me in his arms\Nand sobbed his heart out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I was happier about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you can't decide on something,\Nyou always choose logic over emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then when everything's over,\Nyou start panicking or crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you feeling right now, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are Siluca and I to you, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,pledged to serve the wandering Lord,\NSir Theo, and helped him rise to emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You set a fine example for all Mages.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aishela...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been protecting Siluca in my place,\Nwhen I've wanted to, but couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, and now, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're both my precious daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not a Meletes anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll draw a proposal\Nfor the Imperial Army's reorganization,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so Father, can you please prepare\Nthe Lords' official marching orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Aishela, I want you to get some rest\Nwhile you can, before tomorrow's march.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:12:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew that I'd get to spend time\Nwith Father and Aishela again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Siluca.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wake up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly the way it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just tried to kill Siluca.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then I was planning to kill Theo Cornaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is some kind of new joke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it was the Mage Academy's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,secret agency ordered you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you were a spy all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca, the secret agency\Nhas had their eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been reporting every move you've made,\Nand every plot you've hatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Thank goodness you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Well, I was never ordered to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to cause a disturbance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a hidden organization\Nwithin the secret agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's called Pandora.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pandora?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I received an order from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To murder Theo Cornaro and Siluca Meletes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so I carried it out, and failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But one thing isn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You failed on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there were better ways to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, both Siluca and I were asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you were going to fail on purpose,\NI think you should've just ignored the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't just disobey them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Siluca.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could you take a look at my left breast?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A magic circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did they cast a geas on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I disobey the organization's orders,\Nthis magic circle will stop my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a heinous act.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Siluca.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But once I received the order to kill you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there was no other option.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because if I said anything,\Nthis would've activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I wouldn't be able to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aishela!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C-Curse-breaker spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's not enough time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She is not destined to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Priscilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Holy Grail of Farnese?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Priscilla! Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see, I did what was required of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a holy maiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then would you like to join\Nthe Order of the Holy Crest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful that you saved me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but now that I've lost my Art,\NI won't be able to save Siluca anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I might be executed\Nfor attempting to murder the emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since you failed on purpose,\Nit's not even an attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In a sense,\Nyou risked your life to protect Siluca and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what makes you so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will you tell us all about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can talk about it now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the hidden organization,\NPandora, ordered the assassination.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And those people were also involved\Nin the Great Hall Tragedy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was our organization that made\Nthe Black Witch Jana summon the Demon Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pandora is made up of back-alley Mages\Nwho'd been eliminated, and dropouts like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also collaborators\Nwho pledged loyalty, like Jana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal was to control Chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And not to bring the Ultimate Chaos?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And who would benefit if that happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, it would be troublesome\Nif the Chaos was extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because magic can't be cast anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that's part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We were told that Pandora was carrying out\Nthe Mage Academy's true founding philosophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Supervision of the Lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or their management.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think they've been expunging Lords\Nwho came close to becoming emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would the Mage Academy\Nnot want the Chaos to be extinguished?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the part about\Nthe Mage Academy's true founding philosophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:18:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand\Nwhy they ever needed such a philosophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still not convinced that it's only because of\Nthe loss of their magical abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's a good enough reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of people living in fear\Nof losing the powers they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That vampire king was the same way, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for Lords and Artists.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Pandora\Nhas more collaborators than you'd think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A message, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A commotion has broken out\Nat each of the three factions' camps.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hearing that several Lords and Artists\Nhave been rampaging as if crazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have to make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.64,0:19:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although I can't do much without my Art.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll do what I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to put you through so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And also, thank you, for protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Well, we're family, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I would risk my life any time\Nif it's for my adorable little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I don't think even real families would do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's because they're only related by blood,\Nnothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. You and I aren't related by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why\Nwe have to keep our family ties strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's only the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aishela, you're forgetting Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's on our side now,\Nso you can see him anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But he is family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to be his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.27,0:21:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What you were worried about\Ncame to pass, Lady Marrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Not that I wanted to be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Lords who were used, then discarded\Nby the secret agency, I feel so terrible for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Grancrest that much\Nof a nuisance to the Mage Academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of power\Nthe Grancrest has.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's set our sights\Non defeating the Mage Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't consider ourselves\Nfully prepared to invade Eramu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, we have no choice but to do it,\Nand losing isn't an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if the Academy's wrong,\Nor if the Lords are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But at the very least,\Nwe have the people's support.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.86,0:22:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow morning,\Nlet's commence our march on Eramu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PURGE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 22\NTHE HOLY GRAIL
